    "description": "<i>Fun for family &amp; friends!</i><br><strong>Nicely Dicely</strong> is a fun local multiplayer game based on physics, for up to four simultaneous players. You can decide, if you want to compete against all other players or in teams. Each player controls a player cube on a dynamically changing playing board.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198890/extras/9f66a2a3df244479ee232c4f7b972197.poster.avif?t=1683095635\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198890/extras/9f66a2a3df244479ee232c4f7b972197.webm?t=1683095635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198890/extras/9f66a2a3df244479ee232c4f7b972197.mp4?t=1683095635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There are also passive score cubes, explosive mines and from time to time a mystery crystal, triggering random events on touch. To score, you need to push the other cubes off the board or steal points from other players by paralyzing them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198890/extras/f718cf2ab45d12c1c2382ac82d297908.poster.avif?t=1683095635\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198890/extras/f718cf2ab45d12c1c2382ac82d297908.webm?t=1683095635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198890/extras/f718cf2ab45d12c1c2382ac82d297908.mp4?t=1683095635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join the official  and get in touch!",
